process1.title: Initial Inquiry
process1.description: Potential client contacts the company expressing interest in their services

process1.title: On-site Visit
process1.description: Company representative visits the client's site to assess the project

process1.title: Estimate
process1.description: Company provides a detailed estimate of the project cost to the client

process1.title: Contract Signing
process1.description: Client agrees to the estimate and signs a contract with the company to begin work

process2.title: Online Inquiry
process2.description: Potential client submits an online inquiry form expressing interest in the company's services

process2.title: Phone Consultation
process2.description: A company representative contacts the client to discuss their requirements and answer any initial questions

process2.title: Proposal Submission
process2.description: The company prepares and submits a detailed proposal outlining the scope, timeline, and cost of the project

process2.title: Negotiation
process2.description: The company and the client engage in negotiations to finalize the project details and terms

process2.title: Contract Signing
process2.description: Both parties agree on the terms and conditions and sign a contract to initiate the project
